The function of the equalizer: Media volume control. Equalizer presets. Bass enhancement effect. Five-band equalizer controller. Enable/disable the power mode option for the effect. Equalizer speakers. Five-band music equalizer. Bass booster for headphones. The Bass Booster allows you to adjust the volume to get the best results from your phone. The music showcase plays music and presents beautiful visualizations. Allows you to adjust the volume to get the best results from your phone. An excellent volume control app that controls all volume streams on your Android phone. Make media files produce high quality sound and digital surround support! The perfect booster to maximize volume, listen to your favorite songs and playlists, and revisit your music! Customize your music listening experience with Equalizer and Bass Booster, feeling like never before!

What is VPN A virtual private network (VPN) extends a private network across a public network, and enables users to send and receive data across shared or public networks as if their computing devices were directly connected to the private network. Applications running across the VPN may therefore benefit from the functionality, security, and management of the private network. Individual Internet users may secure their transactions with a VPN, to circumvent geo-restrictions and censorship, or to connect to proxy servers for the purpose of protecting personal identity and location. However, some Internet sites block access to known VPN technology to prevent the circumvention of their geo-restrictions. VPNs cannot make online connections completely anonymous, but they can usually increase privacy and security. To prevent disclosure of private information, VPNs typically allow only authenticated remote access using tunneling protocols and encryption techniques. Mobile virtual private networks are used in settings where an endpoint of the VPN is not fixed to a single IP address.

description: Apply music genre-based equalizer presets or quickly create your own custom presets using a 5-band equalizer controller. The bass equalizer allows you to adjust the sound level so you can get the best music or audio from your phone. Other supported audio effects include: bass booster, virtualizer and reverb preset. The function of the equalizer: Media volume control. Equalizer presets. Bass enhancement effect. Five-band equalizer controller. Enable/disable the power mode option for the effect. Equalizer speakers. Five-band music equalizer. Bass booster for headphones. The Bass Booster allows you to adjust the volume to get the best results from your phone. Increase the volume of any audio device with a single touch. The sound booster really perfects your EQ music listening experience. The music showcase plays music and presents beautiful visualizations. Allows you to adjust the volume to get the best results from your phone. An excellent volume control app that controls all volume streams on your Android phone. Make media files produce high quality sound and digital surround support! The perfect booster to maximize volume, listen to your favorite songs and playlists, and revisit your music! Customize your music listening experience with Equalizer and Bass Booster, feeling like never before!

description: Are you trying to learn chemistry on the go? Meet Complete chemistry and periodic table app that was specifically design to carter for the need of chemistry learners and hobbyist. It covers different parts of chemistry. It gives you to ability to use some interactive chemistry tools like periodic table, chemistry calculator and virtual lab to learn and practice chemistry. In other to practice what you are learning, each chemistry sub-topic comes with mini-quiz that evaluates your understanding of what you have studied. Complete chemistry has a rich community of chemistry lovers interested in learning and sharing knowledge with each other. The daily activity part provides users the chance to solve one chemistry question daily and keep improving their understanding of chemistry. We are constantly working on Complete chemistry to provide more useful materials and resources. Your feedback will help us make it even much better. We are also planning to cover many different chemistry exams from different countries in the world. At present we are adding exams from the following examination bodies - WAEC, NECO, JAMB, WASSCE, SSCE, UTME, KCSE, Grade 9 to Grade 12, AP Chenmistry, Chemistry GCE A'L and O'LPost JAMB and GCE. Complete chemistry features Chemistry Tutorials and Lessons 1. Inorganic chemistry 2. Organic Chemistry 3. Physical Chemistry 4. Analytic Chemistry Chemistry Question and Answer Section 1. Share 2. Teach 3. Learn Daily Chemistry Challenge 1. Solve one chemistry question a day Chemistry Tools 1. Peroidic Table 2. Chemistry calculators 3. Solubility Table 4. Balance Equation 5. Chemistry Glossary 6. Electronic Configuration Chemistry Pro version We are working hard to bring in more exciting features for pro version of Complete chemistry. Below is what you will get if you join the pro membership. 1. Chemistry virtual lab 2. Machine Learning chemistry question auto solver 3. Chemistry Homework helper from experience tutors 4. Chemistry document sharing 5. No ad. Feedback If you have any suggests or feedback, we will be glad to hear from you. You can get in contact with us by using any of these channels below. Email – henry@inducesmile.com Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/InduceSmile

What is VPN A virtual private network (VPN) extends a private network across a public network, and enables users to send and receive data across shared or public networks as if their computing devices were directly connected to the private network. Applications running across the VPN may therefore benefit from the functionality, security, and management of the private network. Individual Internet users may secure their transactions with a VPN, to circumvent geo-restrictions and censorship, or to connect to proxy servers for the purpose of protecting personal identity and location. However, some Internet sites block access to known VPN technology to prevent the circumvention of their geo-restrictions. VPNs cannot make online connections completely anonymous, but they can usually increase privacy and security. To prevent disclosure of private information, VPNs typically allow only authenticated remote access using tunneling protocols and encryption techniques. Mobile virtual private networks are used in settings where an endpoint of the VPN is not fixed to a single IP address.

description: Real Cricket™ Premier League is here and here to stay! For all you cricket fans out there, Intensity of a Real Cricket™ game, now on your mobile!!! Welcome to the most complete Real Cricket™ experience capturing each drop of the Indian Premier League festival. FOR THE FIRST TIME EVER! ALL NEW AUCTION MODE For the First Time Players can manage their favorite franchise and build out a fresh squad in a true to life detailed auction, and taste things from an owners angle! UNIQUE AND NOVEL PREMIER LEAGUE CHALLENGE Play out Historical Scenarios from the previous seasons of the Premier League GEAR UP FOR THE 2017 PREMIER LEAGUE Pad up and guide your favorite teams complete with up to date squads to the ultimate prize ROAD TO REAL CRICKET PREMIER LEAGUE MODE Play each year of the Premier League and choose to write or re-write history by taking your team to the top. Complete with squads from the time. ALL NEW PLAYER PROFILE Track all yours Stats and Increase you’re Rank. Be the Best FRESH LOOK AND FEEL The game is now smoother than ever and with the most stunning presentation. ULTRA FLUID SIGNATURE REAL CRICKET™ ANIMATIONS Scintillating 2D Motion Captured animations ALL NEW ‘GAMECHANGER’ OPTION Players Can Now Download and Pick Batting Shots and Bowling Actions. Load of customization options available and even more on the way… BE STRIKING WITH AUTHENTIC CRICKET EQUIPMENT Authentic Cricket equipment provided by legendary manufacturers – Gray-Nicolls and SS Cricket. ALL NEW HARDCORE DIFFICULTY Want the Game to Be Harder. Well we tried! It’s your turn now… This app offers in-app purchases. Known Issues: - Performance could suffer on some devices with less than recommended device requirements We are here to stay and work to best to provide you with the most dreamlike gameplay on your mobile. *Permissions: To deliver the best experience we would need some permissions from our users: GET_ACCOUNTS: This permission is required to access Google Game Play Services including Login, Achievements and Leaderboard. ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION: We need this permission to detect your location so as to provide region specific content as well as analyze your regions needs and feedback better. WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE and READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE: We need these permissions to cache and read game content during the gameplay. READ_PHONE_STATE: We need this permission to serve you relevant notifications on various updates and offers. RECORD_AUDIO: This is required for Zapr SDK which is integrated within this app to analyze offline TV viewing data and serve media-targeted ads. If you'd like to opt-out of this targeting, please visit the following link: http://www.zapr.in/privacy/.

description: The Music Bass Equalizer lets you adjust the level of sound so you can get the best music or audio from your phone. Apply music genre-based equalizer presets or quickly create your own custom presets using a 5-band equalizer controller. Other audio effects supported include: bass booster, virtualizer and reverb presets. The function of the equalizer: 1. Media volume control. 2. 10 equalizer preset. 3. Bass boost effect. 4. Lock the media volume. 5. 5 band equalizer controller. 6. Stereo LED VU meter. 7. The power mode option for enabling/disabling effects. 8. Equalizer loudspeakers. 9. Five-band music equalizer. 10. Play the local music in this app. A bass booster for headphones. Bass Booster allows you to adjust the sound level to get the best results from your phone. Increase the volume of any audio device with a single touch. The sound booster really perfects your EQ music listening experience. The music showcase plays music and presents beautiful visualizations. 💿 Bass booster: Allows you to adjust the sound level to get the best results from your phone. 💿 Volume booster: An excellent volume control app that controls all volume streams on your Android phone. 💿 Virtual machine: Make media files produce high quality sound with digital surround support! The perfect booster to maximize volume, listen to your favorite songs and playlists, and revisit your music! Customize your music listening experience with Equalizer and Bass Booster, feeling like never before!
